Package: pyShinyCell
Type: Package
Title: Python-Enhanced Shiny Web Apps for Single-Cell Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yang Hu
Maintainer: Yang Hu <hu.yang@nyu.edu>
Description: Extension of ShinyCell that integrates Python analysis tools
    (scanpy, gseapy) with interactive Shiny web applications for single-cell
    genomics. Provides automated H5AD conversion, differential expression analysis,
    gene set enrichment, correlation analysis, and TCR/repertoire visualization.
License: GPL-3
